{
  "stem": "25288.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people occupied the-- the-- the radio station, and so-and-so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And next day on the paper, we saw that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And next day, the Russian came in, or a couple days after-- two days after.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Russian came in, and they were marching through the town with big tanks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were occupied larger, bigger towns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the revolution.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we heard this-- this friend of ours told us-- so before, a friend of mine, who had a position not far from the-- from the Austrian border, he came home to see his mother.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he told his [INAUDIBLE] whenever you want to leave this country, I can help you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when I decided, I went to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I went down to this little town, where my friend-- and I told him, it's the time, here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I want to leave with my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was Wednesday.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Friday-- Monday, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, Saturday, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] make sure you be here Saturday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm going to pick you by the railroad station at that time, that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a Thursday evening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I told Ilona, we are leaving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We leave everything here, and we are leaving tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So her sister lived next door, and they come over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We go with you, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we make little-- but we couldn't carry much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the evening, Friday evening, we went to another town with a-- with a taxi, to other town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there we get the train to Budapest, because we didn't want to take the train there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we didn't want people know we are leaving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we arrived in Budapest, and from Budapest to that little town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our friend was waiting us, by the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
